Just want to say, this was awfully nice of you. I'm not entering the contest so you can dismiss me from entry ... yet, wanted to tell you this:

Thanks for giving people the chance to win $10 ... and while $10 worth of RP may not seem like much, it could totally brighten up someone's day when they are low on income (or have no money to spare) while really wanting that specific skin for their main champion. I know the feeling, before I started to work so thanks again for being a good sport to us all. Props to you sir, have an upvote on the thread.

